text: Eunidia olivacea is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1954. It contains the varietas Eunidia olivacea var. trialbosignata.BioLib.cz - Eunidia olivacea. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1954
